  <description type="morphology">Plants 15–30 cm. Stems villous or tomentose, ± woolly, sparsely glandular-stipitate. Leaves: basal blades lanceolate, 50–100(–150) × 8–15(–40) mm, margins coarsely serrate, faces softly villous, tomentose, stipitate-glandular. Heads 1–4. Involucres 8–10 × 12–15 mm. Phyllaries appressed, unequal, bases chartaceous, apices green.</description>
